name: Sharing is caring
description: By sharing life’s sweet and sour moments, relationships can grow closer. This artwork visualizes the saying 'sharing is caring'. This is the most important message behind the 6-part lemon nft collection. To give love and acceptance to everybody around you. ‘Sharing is caring’ is the sixth and last nft in the lemon collection which tells a story in 6 illustrations. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
